        "ggczQlFQuMx_text": "<p>☀️ <strong>More energy, focus with no jitters</strong></p><p>🥥 <strong>Delicious coconut and vanilla flavours</strong></p><p>🥛 <strong>Super easy to mix with milk, water etc</strong></p><p>✨ <strong>Glowing skin, hair &amp; nails support</strong></p>",
